Function Reference/screen icon « WordPress Codex
-----------

Outputs the return from
[get\_screen\_icon()](/Function_Reference/get_screen_icon "Function Reference/get screen icon"),
which is the HTML tag with icon-32 background class for a screen.

Parameters
----------

 `$screen` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Screen name
    Default: empty string

Source File
-----------

screen\_icon() is located in `wp-admin/includes/screen.php`

